{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way the Germans called them, the terrorists.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as the liberation was approaching, we lost track of time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is, we would be awakened at two o'clock in the morning, four o'clock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lost track of time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our day was completely dislocated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would go to sleep with our clothes on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and while the bombs were falling all of us, and the shooting was going on, we would have our arms like this in the cross, praying Christ to spare us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I understand a lot of people in the convent were killed, children and nuns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And occasionally, we'd go by the body and pay respect to body.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were quite a few funerals that took place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a lot of children died from illness, loneliness, salvation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These were the children, quote, 'unwanted.' Some of them nobody ever came to see them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The one thing I learned, because I, I think at that moment being Jewish wasn't such a thing I-- with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, it was something we were going to keep it a secret and never mention.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I was aware of the suffering [SOBBING] of all the children in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All of us were hungry, and lonely, and starving, and afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And no parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, we were on the mercy of whoever took care of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in a sense, I was very fortunate, because the, the older children took care of the younger one all the way down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So to some degree, there was affection and caring going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
